data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Second Chance Alert!! Transform this gem into your dream home. Three spacious bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, and a prime spot in the coveted Hampton Hills neighborhood. The well-designed kitchen flows seamlessly into the living area and patio, perfect for indoor-outdoor living. Relish convenience in Lakeland's heart, minutes from shopping, dining, medical hubs, and major highways connecting you to Tampa and Orlando. Enhanced security with a pre-installed system. Plus, enjoy the benefits of an affordable HOA. Seize this chance. Schedule a showing now!"
